countries <- c(
  "China", "India", "United States",
  "Indonesia", "Brazil", "Pakistan",
  "Bangladesh", "Nigeria", "Japan")

Econ_of_con %>% 
  filter(country %in% countries) %>% 
  ggplot() +
  aes(x = year, y = lifeExp, color = country,) +
  facet_wrap(~country, scales = "free_y") +
  geom_line()
